<ValidationObserver
  v-slot="{ errors }"
  tag="div"
>
  <input-form
    title="Phila UI Form"
    description="My form description"
    :errors="errors"
  >
    <vee-textbox
      v-model="myTextbox"
      mode="eager"
      rules="required"
    />
    <button
      slot="submit"
      class="is-cta button"
      @click.prevent=""
    >
      Submit
    </button>
  </input-form>
</ValidationObserver>
